name: script-test-coverage-pattern
description: "Patterns for adding mock-only unit tests to Python utility scripts — covering subprocess-heavy, filesystem-heavy, and pure-function scripts in ProjectScylla. Raises scripts/ test coverage from 29% to 65% (10/34 → 22/34 scripts tested)."
category: testing
