| Metric | Before | After |
| -------- | -------- | ------- |
| Tests in file | 114 | 119 |
| Full suite tests | 3185 | 3190 |
| Project coverage | ~78% | 78.36% |
| cmd_run() flow coverage | gaps | tiers + max_subtests verified |
| cmd_repair() branch coverage | missing | skip-existing + corrupt-JSON covered |
```
